Third-party notice:
This repository depends on third-party software components that are NOT
redistributed as part of this source tree. They are pulled at install or
runtime from their upstream sources:
- Python packages listed in `requirements.txt` (installed from PyPI)
- `pySim` (Osmocom) - an optional on-disk checkout when the SAIP ASN.1
  compile path or the SCP11-local flows are exercised; clone manually from
  `https://gitlab.com/osmocom/pysim.git` into `pysim/` at the repository
  root. The directory is gitignored and is NOT redistributed with this
  project. Runtime falls back to the installed `pySim` PyPI wheel when the
  checkout is absent.
- Optional external system tooling such as `gpg` (when encrypted inventory
  payloads are enabled) and `osmo-remsim-client-st2` / SIMtrace2 firmware
  (when the HIL bridge is in use). These tools are provided by their
  respective upstream projects and are not redistributed here.

Vendored schema notice:
The only third-party material redistributed inside this tree is the RSPRO
ASN.1 schema at `docs/RSPRO.asn` (mirrored into `Tools/HilBridge/RSPRO.asn`
for wheel packaging). It is included because it is required at runtime by
the HIL bridge decoder and is too small to justify a separate installation
step.

